<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width">
    <title>Password Change Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body { 
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h2>Password Changed Successfully</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{username}},</p>
        
        <p>This email confirms that your password was successfully changed on {{dateTime}}.</p>
        
        <p>If you did not make this change, please contact our support team immediately at {{supportEmail}} or by replying to this email.</p>

        <p>For security reasons, we recommend:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Regularly updating your password</li>
            <li>Not sharing your password with anyone</li>
            <li>Using unique passwords for different accounts</li>
        </ul>

        <p>Best regards,<br>
        The {{companyName}} Team</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>